    "folder": "NPC Generator / Human / Damaran",
    "description": "<p>A faith table weighted for Damaran humans. A hardy, stubborn, and resilient people from the cold, harsh lands of the North, their faith is centered on survival, endurance, and protection. Ilmater, the god of suffering and endurance, is their foremost patron. Deities of agriculture (Chauntea), protection (Helm, Torm), and battle (Tempus) are also vital for their survival. They pray to Lathander for the coming of spring and propitiate Auril out of fear of the brutal winters.</p>",
