    "description": "<p>A faith table weighted for the Tuigans. As a nomadic horde of warriors from the vast eastern plains, their faith is centered on conquest, war, and the natural forces of their homeland. Tempus, the god of battle, is their chief deity. The orc gods Gruumsh (conquest) and Ilneval (hordes) are also commonly revered for their martial prowess. The endless sky (Akadi) is a powerful animistic force, while gods of tyranny (Bane), the hunt (Malar), and destruction (Talos) appeal to their warlike culture.</p>",
