    "description": "<p>A faith table weighted for Tieflings. Shunned by society, a tiefling's faith is often a personal and defiant choice. While a significant number embrace their heritage and worship Asmodeus, many others gravitate towards deities of outcasts and survivors. Mask, Tymora, Shar, and Ilmater are common patrons, representing the different paths a tiefling might take: stealth, luck, bitterness, or endurance. Gods of war and ambition like Tempus and Bane also attract those who seek power to overcome their plight.</p>",
